1169
01:18:13.012 --> 01:18:14.304
Don't listen to your father!

1170
01:18:14.388 --> 01:18:16.264
Timothy, Timothy.
Look at me. Don't listen to Coach Cal.


1171
01:18:16.348 --> 01:18:17.932
Move your feet. Move around!

1172
01:18:18.142 --> 01:18:20.560
