01:18:22.021 --> 01:18:23.354
Come on, move around!

1175
01:18:23.480 --> 01:18:25.857
Chase the ball! Come on!

1176
01:18:27.192 --> 01:18:29.861
Way to go. Way to
go. Way to go, Tim.

