01:18:53.302 --> 01:18:54.510
God, he's doing that thing again.

1178
01:18:54.595 --> 01:18:57.138
No, no. Put your arms down. Arms down.

1179
01:18:57.222 --> 01:18:58.348
Get your head in the game, baby!

1180
01:18:58.432 --> 01:18:59.432
Get your head in the game.

1181
01:18:59.516 --> 01:19:01.100
Get in the game!

1182
01:19:01.185 --> 01:19:03.269
Like we worked it, come on!

1183
01:19:25.626 --> 01:19:27.502
There you go, Erasers,
there you go!


1184
01:19:27.628 --> 01:19:28.961
Yes! Yes!

