01:20:13.382 --> 01:20:15.466
Get that kid! Put him on the ground!

1202
01:20:16.260 --> 01:20:18.553
Take his knees out!
Put him on the ground!


1203
01:20:21.056 --> 01:20:23.391
See? See?

