01:20:23.475 --> 01:20:25.476
See what happens
when you're there for your kid!


1205
01:20:25.561 --> 01:20:27.353
Huh? See what happens
when you believe in him! Huh?


1206
01:20:27.438 --> 01:20:31.023
I could have been like that,
because I had skills, but no.


1207
01:20:31.108 --> 01:20:33.568
Come on, Timothy! Go! Go!

1208
01:20:33.652 --> 01:20:35.069
Go, Timothy! Go!

